      <title>卢比奥称美国国际开发署摇摇欲坠，他现在负责该机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/rubio-says-he-s-now-in-charge-of-usaid-as-relief-agency-teeters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府及其盟友让高级职员休假并威胁永久关闭美国国际开发署后，国务卿马尔科·卢比奥表示，他现在负责管理美国国际开发署。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/rubio-says-he-s-now-in-charge-of-usaid-as-relief-agency-teeters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 17:33:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国称阿斯利康因工厂资金纠纷削减疫苗研发承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/astrazeneca-cut-vaccine-r-d-pledge-in-plant-funding-row-uk-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位部长表示，阿斯利康公司将英国新疫苗工厂的研发计划支出从 1.5 亿英镑削减至约 9000 万英镑（1.12 亿美元），这一投资决定导致政府为现已放弃的该项目提供更少的政府资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/astrazeneca-cut-vaccine-r-d-pledge-in-plant-funding-row-uk-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 17:14:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉总统马查多称特朗普与马杜罗的沟通“积极”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/venezuela-s-machado-says-trump-channel-with-maduro-is-positive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉反对派领导人玛丽亚·科里娜·马查多表示，她与总统唐纳德·特朗普的特使进行了交谈，后者在上周与总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗会晤后确保释放六名美国囚犯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/venezuela-s-machado-says-trump-channel-with-maduro-is-positive</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 17:00:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与 Sheinbaum 谈话后将墨西哥关税推迟一个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexico-s-sheinbaum-says-tariffs-delayed-for-a-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普周一与美国贸易代表克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆进行会谈后同意将对墨西哥征收 25% 的关税推迟一个月，这对于濒临贸易战的邻国来说是一个戏剧性的转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexico-s-sheinbaum-says-tariffs-delayed-for-a-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 15:26:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国总理冒着遭到谴责的风险强行通过预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/french-premier-forces-through-budget-risking-no-confidence-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁周一绕过议会下院，强行通过了 2025 年预算法案，而宪法中规定可能会引发不信任投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/french-premier-forces-through-budget-risking-no-confidence-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 15:22:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝森特出任CFPB代理负责人，暂停规则和诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/bessent-to-temporarily-lead-cfpb-after-chopra-s-ouster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长斯科特·贝森特（Scott Bessent）目前担任美国消费者金融保护局代理局长，这表明美国政府可能会转变罗希特·乔普拉（Rohit Chopra）领导下的激进执法和监管方式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/bessent-to-temporarily-lead-cfpb-after-chopra-s-ouster</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 14:42:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯向白厅各部门发出“现金持平”的紧缩警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/austerity-risk-as-rachel-reeves-gives-departments-budget-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政部已要求多个政府部门在六月份计划进行的重大支出审查之前做好冻结现金预算的准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/austerity-risk-as-rachel-reeves-gives-departments-budget-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 14:31:29 GMT</pubDate>
